        "citation": "Little A. Review: antibiotics are not effective for upper respiratory tract infection in children [commentary on Fahey T, Stocks N, Thomas T. Systematic review of the treatment of upper respiratory tract infection. ARCH DIS CHILD 1998 Sep;79:225-30]. Evidence Based Nursing. 1999;:77-77.",
        "id": "7bf3e1ee3e452081d62aa966e900832447e46a9d",
