        "citation": "Karsch-Völk M, Bruce Barrett, David Kiefer, Rudolf Bauer, Karin Ardjomand‐Woelkart, Klaus Linde. Echinacea for preventing and treating the common cold. Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews. 2014;2(2):CD000530.",
