        "citation": "Hemila H., Petrus E.J., Fitzgerald J.T., Prasad A.. Zinc acetate lozenges for treating the common cold: an individual patient data meta-analysis. British Journal of Clinical Pharmacology. 2016;82(5):1393-1398.",
