        "citation": "An IM De Sutter, Mieke L van Driel, Anna A Kumar, Olivia Lesslar, Alja Skrt. Oral antihistamine‐decongestant‐analgesic combinations for the common cold. Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews. 2012;2(2):CD004976.",
        "id": "2b88290194045684aeec654c5de658a51ae56009",
