        "citation": "Timmer A, Günther J, Motschall E, Rücker G, Antes G, Kern WV. Pelargonium sidoides extract for treating acute respiratory tract infections. Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews. 2013;10(10):CD006323.",
        "id": "956804349d4ec5bf0f0c4028de5e6ad07b03bd6e",
